ACTING NOW TRAINING & BUSINESS LINKAGE REPORT

Author

Emile Mawutor Tsekpo

1 Introduction

Acting Now seeks to boost the production of locally grown nutritious foods on local in Ghana by reducing vulnerability of farmers to climate and economic shocks. The main goal of the project is to build more resilient farms and food systems that are prepared for future climate change impacts or economic vulnerabilities.

As part of efforts to improve farm productivity, farmers were trained on Climate Smart Agriculture (CSA) by various trainers and district Agricultural Extension Officers.

This report presents an update on Climate Smart Agriculture Trainings in Ghana, Nigeria, Sierra Leone.
